{"tid":247798,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"黑客盜取未上映《加勒比海盜5》勒索迪士尼","createTime":"2017-05-18T05:43:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T06:58:23.000Z","uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b0f4ed25a4adadc6cc892f143717f7b77f79ba5c","tid":247798,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T05:43:28.000Z","msg":"由荷里活男星尊尼特普（Johnny Depp）主演的《加勒比海盜：惡靈啟航》（Pirates of the Caribbean：Dead Men Tell No Tales）將於下周五（5月26日）上映，不過據稱黑客已經盜取完整的電影，向迪士尼電影公司勒索天價網上貨幣比特幣，如果不付款就會在網上公開電影。電影上周四曾在上海舉行世界首映禮。<br />\n<br />\n聯邦調查局（FBI）目前正在進行調查，迪士尼卻無意向黑客低頭，絕對不會交出贖金。迪士尼行政總裁Bob Iger雖然沒有公開黑客掌握了那套電影，但昨日於紐約一個市政廳會議，曾向美國廣播公司（ABC）員工表示某片被黑客盜取，如果不交贖金，黑客就會逐步公開電影片段，起初公開5分鐘，之後每次公開20分鐘。而Deadline網站證實該片就是《加勒比海盜：惡靈啟航》。<br />\n<br />\n上月Netflix電視台亦曾被黑客盜取《Orange is the New Black》第5季的10集，勒索巨款，但被Netflix拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170516/bkn-20170516094417843-0516_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170516%2Fbkn-20170516094417843-0516_00862_001.html&d=PGvktPFvO8uhCwWWOTiXtUjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=1a86f31a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170516/bkn-20170516094417843-0516_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b2150f293d43efcc4cc3d880009fcca1a64907","tid":247798,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T05:45:40.000Z","msg":"鐘意日本果個多d"},{"pid":"8d36b2633d0073cd86dd8651410d9092d07ef44e","tid":247798,"uid":33456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T06:58:23.000Z","msg":"公開左照去戲院睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}